data.description: You'll love this charming home located in the neighborhood of Riverwalk! Nestled on a .17 acre lot with beautiful limestone masonry, which is only the beginning of the warm welcome this home offers. With 1,852 square feet of spacious living, this home has four bedrooms and two baths.   When you enter this home, you are greeted with a welcoming family room with gorgeous luxury vinyl plank flooring and many windows. Your living room features a ceiling fan and shelving perfect for an entertainment center, and you can showcase your treasures.   Your kitchen is perfect for your resident chef, with lovely quartz counters and loads of cabinet space. You have a shelving unit in your breakfast area: tile backsplash, smooth electric cooktop stove, and a built-in microwave.   Your spacious master is serene and relaxing, with windows that allow loads of natural light, plush carpet, and a ceiling fan.   The ensuite features a double vanity, walk-in shower, and luxurious soaking tub.   Your second bedroom has luxury vinyl plank floors and a ceiling fan. Your third bedroom has plush carpets and a ceiling fan. Your fourth bedroom has luxury vinyl plank,  shiplap, and a chair rail. Your secondary bath has an extended vanity and a tub/ shower combo.   Your laundry room has ample space for storage.   When it's time to relax, venture to the lovely backyard and extended covered patio or entertain in style on your extended patio with a stone pathway. You have a spot with power for a hot tub!  You have a shed to store all of your gardening tools. This lovely home is situated in the highly coveted area of Hutto ISD. Updates: In 2023, AC repairs include adding a UV light to the system. The sellers have added a wall unit in the dining room and living room. TV mount, two refrigerators, a washer, and a dryer will be conveyed with the sale. Close to nearby Hutto Lake Park, major roads, great restaurants, plenty of shopping, and much more. Welcome home!
